candidates.title: feat: add tracing instrumentation
fix: correct parallel archive extract failures
feat: add reqwest backoff/retry logic and tracing support
chore: remove use of copy left license MPL-2.0 from dependencies
fix: update dependencies to address RUSTSEC-2024-0020
chore: update dependencies
fix!: remove bundled as a default feature and corrected bug when the bundled feature is not used
refactor!: refactor status to check on demand instead of attempting to track the state dynamically
docs: add postgres driver and sqlx examples
chore: update action permissions to reduce write privilege scope
refactor: update psql to manage setting the PGPASSWORD environment variable when pg_password is set
test: add benchmarks
chore: update windows to use UTF8 to align with other operating systems and utilize capabilities of the newer releases from https://github.com/theseus-rs/postgresql-binaries
docs: add postgres to keywords
refactor!: remove archive hash from the public interface and always calculate/verify the has when requesting an archive
chore: add examples
docs: update cargo description
docs: enable documentation features
Update public API
candidates.body: Remove the "pub" modified from the postgresql module as all relevant constructs are exported with "pub use"

labels.description: Pull requests that update a dependency file

candidates.body:
Bumps [tempfile](https://github.com/Stebalien/tempfile) from 3.9.0 to 3.10.0.
Changelog

Sourced from tempfile's changelog.

3.10.0

  • Drop redox_syscall dependency, we now use rustix for Redox.
  • Add Builder::permissions for setting the permissions on temporary files and directories (thanks to @​Byron).
  • Update rustix to 0.38.31.
  • Update fastrand to 2.0.1.
Commits
  • 61531ea chore: release v3.10.0
  • e246c4a chore: update deps (#275)
  • 4a05e47 feat: Add Builder::permissions() method. (#273)
  • 184ab8f fix: drop redox_syscall dependency (#272)
  • See full diff in compare view
